entries.help_text:
This is the actual macro definition.

Here is an example macro:
Hi there;
/stand;
/pause 3;
/bow %TT;

The first line is a text string that is spoken as spacial chat.  The second line calls the command Stand.  The third line makes the macro wait 3 seconds.  The final line makes your character bow to your current target.  See your documentation for more information about macros.
